---
import Card from "../../unitComponents/Card.astro";
import LearnBtn from "../../unitComponents/LearnBtn.astro";
import Planos from "../../../assets/images/planos.webp";
import logo from "../../../assets/images/About/Improvement/ANSYS_logo.webp";
import IAD1 from "../../../assets/images/About/Improvement/IAD1.webp";
import IAD2 from "../../../assets/images/About/Improvement/IAD2.webp";
import IAD3 from "../../../assets/images/About/Improvement/IAD3.webp";
import IAD4 from "../../../assets/images/About/Improvement/IAD4.webp";
import CD1 from "../../../assets/images/About/Improvement/CD1.webp";
import CD2 from "../../../assets/images/About/Improvement/CD2.webp";
import CD3 from "../../../assets/images/About/Improvement/CD3.webp";
import CD4 from "../../../assets/images/About/Improvement/CD4.webp";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<section class="w-full">
  <div class="w-full flex justify-center">
    <Image src={Planos} alt="" />
  </div>
  <div class="w-full max-w-7xl px-8 mx-auto font-bold my-10">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl text-grisT">
      IMPROVEMENT IN SYSTEMS AND DESIGNS
    </h1>
  </div>
  <div class="max-w-7xl px-8 mx-auto">
    <div class="w-full font-bold">
      <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-grisT">
        All our systems are engineered to meet the highest international
        standards and are carefully tailored to comply with the specific
        regulations of the country or state where the equipment will be
        installed.
      </p><br />
      <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-grisT">
        Our top-tier engineering and design team is composed of specialized,
        experienced engineers who utilize advanced tools and simulation software
        to develop new industrial systems and optimize existing ones.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full font-bold my-16">
      <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-redBg text-center">
        A reliable and productive equipment starts with a perfect and <br
        />detailed design
      </h2><br />
      <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl text-black text-center">
        Our design approach directly addresses common issues and inefficiencies
        found in other brands.
      </h3>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 flex justify-center items-center">
    <Image src={logo} alt="ANSYS Logo" />
  </div>
  <div class="w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 font-bold">
    <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-grisT text-center">
      Using finite element analysis software (AnsysÂ®), we conduct precise tests
      to evaluate the behavior of new designs, improvements to current designs,
      and custom orders through computer simulations. This rigorous testing
      ensures the quality and reliability of our products.
    </p><br />
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 text-base md:text-lg text-grisT">
      <li>
        Behavior of the flow of aggregates and air at any point in the process.
      </li>
      <li>Analysis of temperatures, their use and their isolation.</li>
      <li>
        Analysis of structural, static and dynamic efforts, during the operation
        and in the installation and dismantling maneuvers.
      </li>
      <li>
        Analysis of the behavior of air and dust flow in cyclone separators and
        baghouses for pollution control.
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="w-full flex flex-col justify-center items-center">
    <div
      class="max-w-7xl grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-4 md:grid-cols-4 gap-10 px-8 font-bold text-black text-base md:text-lg my-16"
    >
      <Card>
        <h3 class="text-center">Dust flow in a baghouse</h3>
        <div class="w-full">
          <Image src={IAD1} alt="" class="min-w-full min-h-[250px]" />
        </div>
      </Card>
      <Card>
        <h3 class="text-center">Dust flow in a baghouse</h3>
        <div class="w-full">
          <Image src={IAD2} alt="" class="min-w-full min-h-[250px]" />
        </div>
      </Card>
      <Card>
        <h3 class="text-center">Dust flow in a baghouse</h3>
        <div class="w-full">
          <Image src={IAD3} alt="" class="min-w-full min-h-[250px]" />
        </div>
      </Card>
      <Card>
        <h3 class="text-center">Dust flow in a baghouse</h3>
        <div class="w-full">
          <Image src={IAD4} alt="" class="min-w-full max-h-[250px]" />
        </div>
      </Card>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 font-bold flex flex-col gap-10">
    <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-grisT text-center">
      ...and After the design and manufacturing process, we continue to monitor
      equipment performance through the maintenance services we provide. This
      ongoing feedback allows us to continuously improve future production,
      resulting in some of the most reliable and productive equipment on the
      market.
    </p>
    <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-grisT text-center">Custom Design</h1>
    <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-grisT text-center">
      In addition to our standardized designs, we specialize in customized
      solutions tailored to the specific needs of each client. Whether adapting
      to unique environmental conditions or meeting precise performance
      requirements, our team works closely with customers to develop systems
      that deliver unmatched reliability and efficiency.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="w-full flex flex-col justify-center items-center">
    <div
      class="max-w-7xl grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-10 px-8 font-bold text-black text-base md:text-lg my-10"
    >
      <Card>
        <div>
          <Image src={CD1} alt="" />
        </div>
      </Card>
      <Card>
        <div>
          <Image src={CD2} alt="" />
        </div>
      </Card>
      <Card>
        <div>
          <Image src={CD3} alt="" />
        </div>
      </Card>
      <Card>
        <div>
          <Image src={CD4} alt="" />
        </div>
      </Card>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="flex justify-center pb-10">
    <LearnBtn />
  </div>
</section>
